, Stamatellos et al 2007); (3) The thermal\nrelaxation of temperature fluctuations in an static homogeneous sphere\n(Masunaga et al 1998, Spiegel 1957, Stamatellos et al 2007)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Sep 2008 14:08:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
